name: Check Available Bike Count Matchec Between UI And API
fullName: Tests.Check Available Bike Count Matchec Between UI And API
description:
Reads bike count for specific bike station from the API and UI
and checks that bike count matches between UI and API.
descriptionHtml:
Reads bike count for specific bike station from the API and UI
and checks that bike count matches between UI and API.

testStage.description:
Reads bike count for specific bike station from the API and UI
and checks that bike count matches between UI and API.

steps.name: common.Given I Open HSL Web Page
common.And I Navigate To City Bike View
common.And I Get All Bike Stations From The API
common.When I Read Number Of Available Bikes For The Bike Station "Mestarinkatu"

parameters.name: arg1
parameters.value: msg=Bike station "${bike_station}" not found from API

steps.name: common.And I Go To City Bike Station View And Search Bike Station "Mestarinkatu"
common.And I Read Available Bike Count Value From UI
common.Then I See Available Bike Count Matches Between UI And API

parameters.name: arg3
parameters.value: msg=Bike count in UI and API did not match, UI ${AVAILABLE_BIKE_COUNT_UI} != API ${AVAILABLE_BIKE_COUNT_UI}
